{"tid":1141080,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴：佐真奴是歐洲最好的中場球員","createTime":"2019-05-06T08:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T19:31:27.000Z","uid":132573,"like":72,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"987dc3cfecbacc442797b3bb6eb01425403e15a9","tid":1141080,"uid":132573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:52:58.000Z","msg":"摩連奴接受採訪時稱讚車路士中場佐真奴，他認為佐真奴是歐洲最好的中場球員。<br />\n<br />\n他説道：&ldquo;在我看來，佐真奴是歐洲最好的中場球員。他具備其他任何人都不具備的能力：看他控制比賽節奏的方式，他如何在轉換過程中搶回球權，以及如何承受高強度的壓力，令人難以置信。我沒有看到其他球員能像佐真奴這樣。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n消息參考來源: <a href=\"https://readchelsea.com/2019/05/05/mourinho-jorginho-is-the-best-midfielder-in-europe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freadchelsea.com%2F2019%2F05%2F05%2Fmourinho-jorginho-is-the-best-midfielder-in-europe%2F&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHkXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=9f202e41\" target=\"_blank\">https://readchelsea.com/2019/05/05/mourinho-jorginho-is-the-best-midfielder-in-europe/</a>"},{"pid":"d11d4141b141aebe697b1d8b921f5a0fd5c608d0","tid":1141080,"uid":247905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"一線佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66db8ad07e79e1875c184ae7f91bb13b13698230","tid":1141080,"uid":17387,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"舒服佐"},{"pid":"206ceb4828fafb8664a117c55ddf504c3508d153","tid":1141080,"uid":67225,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"單打普巴成日妹波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19d013888605607f578bb848cc336a5305caa8b","tid":1141080,"uid":40932,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66db8ad07e79e1875c184ae7f91bb13b13698230","tid":1141080,"uid":17387,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"舒服佐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:44:29.000Z","msg":"舒服埋右"},{"pid":"5dbc